content:
Along the Artisan's Street, at moments like this in the afternoon,
when sunlight meets the countless gems in shop windows, {想象中}
it's enough to dazzle any traveler's eyes.

At this hour, all vitality has burned to its peak,
I need to replenish my energy. {短暂停}
(drowsy) I believe it's time for me to rest. Let's chat another time.
